Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:02.10,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,A war is beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.61,0:00:07.52,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,The Holy Capital, with the church this time, has devised a plan to retake Bright Light Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:10.44,Default,OM,0000,0000,0000,,The church is set on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:14.41,Default,OM,0000,0000,0000,,Without the fight against the demons, their power as a unifying force wanes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:17.33,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the papal election also has an effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:21.54,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be more naval skirmishes around Bright Light Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:23.56,Default,OM,0000,0000,0000,,So we're making more compasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:25.36,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,Warships, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:27.96,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,I've taken control of the Tin Country's naval yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.48,0:00:33.93,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,If we gain control of Bright Light Island, we'll be able to open new trade routes to the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:36.93,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,Transporting goods that way will be far cheaper than by land.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:44.19,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,My jurisdiction, the Southern Nations, continues to see gains in productivity, and I don't want that to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:50.44,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,And I've also been asked to provide a large quantity of South Sea herring.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:53.42,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,At least five times my current holdings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:56.45,Default,OM,0000,0000,0000,,Are they planning to build a palace of herring?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.45,0:00:59.45,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,They have a magic spell that changes herring into wheat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:03.08,Default,OM,0000,0000,0000,,So it's that princess, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.08,0:01:05.54,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she's my shining star.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:10.70,Default,OM,0000,0000,0000,,I thought money was the only thing you could ever love.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:15.20,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,However, it'll be a serious problem if we don't succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:17.09,Default,YM,0000,0000,0000,,The war will still benefit us somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:20.68,Default,OM,0000,0000,0000,,The war will last as long as the demons do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:23.89,Default,OM,0000,0000,0000,,And in the south, power changes hands rapidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.89,Default,OM,0000,0000,0000,,All will depend on the war's outcome.
