Dialogue: 1,0:01:38.86,0:01:41.82,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I want to be annoying for you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:41.82,0:01:44.78,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I don't mind being conceited
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.78,0:01:48.82,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Hide a tree in a forest, they say
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.58,0:01:53.33,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}It started with a little mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:01:53.33,0:01:56.33,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Let's redo our meeting from there
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.33,0:02:00.79,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Let's oppose the strand of time
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.55,0:02:06.76,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Strength alone is no weapon
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.84,0:02:14.93,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}You taught me that just now
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.93,0:02:20.44,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I want to show you what lies
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.44,0:02:26.65,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}beyond these days
Dialogue: 1,0:02:26.65,0:02:29.20,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}The wind is strong
Dialogue: 1,0:02:29.20,0:02:32.28,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I'm sure you know that too
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.28,0:02:37.12,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I can't fly
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.12,0:02:43.92,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Sharing makes you dependant
Dialogue: 1,0:02:43.92,0:02:47.09,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Now, take my hand
Dialogue: 1,0:02:47.09,0:02:49.64,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Hold it tight
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.64,0:02:53.93,OP,bord,0000,0000,0000,done,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Now...
