Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:03.24,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:04.24,Default,DG,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.41,Default,DG,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.46,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:14.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Come. I'll give you a chance to make up for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:16.97,Default,OtherGuy,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:17.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.83,0:03:21.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think keeps your town safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.00,0:03:22.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.25,0:03:24.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,She wants you to release her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.84,0:03:27.90,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:37.98,Default,Commander,0000,0000,0000,,The time has come!{and so have I}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:46.70,Default,Commander,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 15 years since the foolish demons first tried to steal our world of light!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.00,0:03:50.96,Default,Commander,0000,0000,0000,,A foolish commander's failed strategy cost us Bright Light Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A grave loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.14,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.84,0:03:58.05,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,You dare to insult the Winter King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:07.72,Default,Commander,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, men...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:11.26,Default,Commander,0000,0000,0000,,Warships have rallied from across the world behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:13.03,Default,Commander,0000,0000,0000,,Two hundred of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:15.04,Default,Commander,0000,0000,0000,,When you valiant warriors board them,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these two hundred ships will stab two hundred daggers into the demons' hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:23.43,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,With this simpleton commanding us, we'll end up losing a war we could easily win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:25.74,Default,Commander,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's time to set sail.{for fail}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.74,0:04:29.66,Default,Commander,0000,0000,0000,,The sun shines for our victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:35.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So the Crusade of the Holy Key's troops run Gate City?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.21,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.11,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What of the forces outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.21,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Do they watch the surrounding area?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:43.57,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,There are four armies...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:45.64,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,They enter the town on a rotation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:49.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What's the difference between the forces outside and those within?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.70,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,When they return, they're rowdy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.06,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,and they do terrible things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:59.94,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,The soldiers in town are the more highly ranked ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:03.24,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,Like the king's children or relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:04.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So mostly nobles?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.88,0:05:09.05,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,So they stay in the safety of the town while taking advantage of the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:10.83,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,Because we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:12.97,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And that gives them power over you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:14.78,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything to stop them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.78,0:05:15.83,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,because we lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:17.68,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what we won?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:25.34,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If the humans win, will the entire demon world end up this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:29.68,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And if the demons win, will the human world end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:30.96,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:34.10,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,The people in the Eastern Fortress don't really do anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:37.72,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,So when the demons run, they always run east.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.24,0:05:39.61,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The Eastern Fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.44,0:05:41.96,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's good information.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:42.94,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.22,0:05:45.25,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:48.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What would the Demon King say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:51.35,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Probably to follow the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:02.42,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,This is a temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.88,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Knight, if you're a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:10.93,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,why are you the Demon King's knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.57,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I belong to the Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.57,0:06:17.23,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,You belong to the Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:17.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:22.19,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,Then you lost to the Demon King...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:27.58,Default,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Die! Die, humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:29.12,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:29.98,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:32.03,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,It's better that you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:32.86,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,You won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:34.04,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,You won't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.04,Default,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:40.19,Default,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You stole our lives! You stole our peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.97,Default,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You took everything from us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:46.39,Default,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You deserve to lie with the maggots!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.12,0:06:44.32,Default,MG,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:45.22,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:49.51,Default,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,May you be cursed for 3,000 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:55.99,Default,Demon,0000,0000,0000,,May the human world be cursed with darkness and Oblivion take you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.06,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What you just said...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.62,0:07:02.59,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You don't belong to someone because they beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:05.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't give them the right to do anything they want to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:10.29,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I belong to the Demon King, but I didn't lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:14.37,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Winning doesn't make you right, and it doesn't mean you can do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:16.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:19.23,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I am
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the path that extends beyond the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:29.59,Default,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,Winter King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:33.14,Default,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,We're meeting with the White Night King's forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:36.76,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we'll make landfall before dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.25,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.83,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:04.04,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:06.49,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,The Winter Fleets will not fall so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.13,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on their vital point and fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.85,Default,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,Ship 18 has sunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:23.56,Default,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,The White Night King's ship, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:35.24,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them sink our flagship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:37.03,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Stop them now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.25,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Going for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:52.06,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:53.73,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:55.26,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I arrived too early...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:58.04,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,So I figured I'd look at the flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.04,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.90,Default,Queen,0000,0000,0000,,A disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.23,0:09:13.65,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0010,,The Winter King died in order for you to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:18.35,Default,WNK,0000,0000,0010,,His sacrifice does not atone for his failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:21.91,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0010,,What happened to your southern warrior's pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:25.29,Default,WNK,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if we lost 200 old, rundown ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.99,0:09:28.79,Default,WNK,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get new ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:33.67,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,My father died doing what he believed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.67,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,That is fine and well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:39.01,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,But responsibility for the defeat is a different matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:43.52,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Your failure to plan ahead cost the lives of 6,000 soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.64,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,As a king, you should know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:48.32,Default,WNK,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:50.47,Default,WNK,0000,0000,0000,,I'll assume responsibility for whatever you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.69,Default,WNK,0000,0000,0000,,However, Winter Prince, I've heard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you have the Lakeside Convent and some scholar
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:10:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bringing you riches you've kept to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:06.21,Default,WNK,0000,0000,0000,,You've also involved the Alliance, and received a large sum of money from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:09.48,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that we've adopted a new method of farming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:13.39,Default,WNK,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you still desire financial support?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:14.80,Default,WNK,0000,0000,0000,,You're a greedy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:17.05,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,This is farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:21.97,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,I take for myself the name of Winter King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:26.93,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Before winter's end, I shall carry out a second plan to retake Bright Light Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:28.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:32.64,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,My weakness meant I had no influence over anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:35.32,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel the weight of this sin on my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.57,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,We pushed a burden that should've been ours
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,upon the shoulders of a single hero
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:45.08,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,and consequently lost his guiding light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:50.08,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,As child of the last king, I will take back Bright Light Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.08,Default,WNK,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}He was a soldier, like any other
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:53.12,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,and bring the Southern Nations some tiny fraction of the light
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the hero was to bring us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:10:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:04.26,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,Send a messenger to her at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.77,Default,WK,0000,0000,0000,,We require a commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.32,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:10.44,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.10,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.94,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's sooner than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.53,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.53,0:11:16.53,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:17.60,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:20.61,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.96,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I only have one other friend of my gender.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.96,0:11:26.24,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And that's the Head Maid, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:28.20,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:30.75,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:32.71,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I've always
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:37.38,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,wanted to be something like a friend to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:40.97,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,This war involves me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:47.35,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to imagine that my will has had a butterfly effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:53.31,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But there are still some things I cannot bring myself to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.93,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,They feel like betrayals to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.57,0:12:00.74,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm lying to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:05.93,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I've been lying to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:09.33,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.55,0:12:15.43,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You know I am the Prioress of the Lakeside Convent, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.43,0:12:16.09,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:19.09,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,And that I serve the Holy Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:25.59,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Then as a servant of the Holy Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.24,0:12:31.48,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I shall hear your confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.74,0:12:35.22,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You have lied to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:37.98,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,You have confessed this to me and to the Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:40.76,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Your sins have been forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:42.99,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,There are no more problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:44.65,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm the Demon King?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:47.28,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Your sin was lying, was it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.28,0:12:52.16,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you think being the Demon King is a sin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:58.76,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Do you regret trying to take the Hero from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:02.17,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Then we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:06.37,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,The Lakeside Convent doesn't like annoying rituals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.36,0:13:08.86,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.85,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,There's no problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:13.64,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:18.44,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,She's the Demon King, but she isn't a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:21.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,She would never go back on her word.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,There's no problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:26.02,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Demon King...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:26.78,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:30.89,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,It's true the Hero made a contract with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:35.29,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps there {\i1}is{\i0} a special bond between you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:38.26,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,But there's more than one kind of bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.17,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero trusted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.91,0:13:42.50,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,That is my treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:44.08,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't betray him either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:54.96,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,With this, we can now be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:58.58,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.76,0:14:05.20,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way in hell I'd fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:10.19,Default,K,0000,0000,0000,,And I won't give up on the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:22.50,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.21,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:28.59,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,A present for the New Year's festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.12,0:14:31.22,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:33.56,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:34.96,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:37.31,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,A doll of the Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:40.75,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,That's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:42.82,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:45.19,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to have this "lily of the valley" perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:47.19,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,That's so nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:48.73,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.73,0:14:51.12,Default,Mh,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:55.22,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us made this for the lady with the glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:56.24,Default,Mh,0000,0000,0000,,For me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:57.12,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a frilled apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:02.04,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,My sister did the embroidering!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.24,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Lily of the valley?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.24,0:15:05.83,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:06.51,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.61,Default,Mh,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:12.68,Default,Mh,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:15.08,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had forgotten all about the festival until you just mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:19.60,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:21.48,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.48,0:15:23.36,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.67,0:15:25.60,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,You've been so kind to us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:28.61,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,and gave us such a warm place to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:32.69,Default,Mb,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we're getting a present every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:37.16,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:43.74,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure you won't go, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:46.30,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I don't like big crowds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:49.96,Default,Ms,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll be leaving you alone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.35,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a whole year.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:59.22,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't touched you for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:02.02,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had the chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.85,0:16:07.20,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And I belong to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.61,0:16:11.08,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I've grown weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:14.16,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid to change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.17,0:16:19.29,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a demon, so war and bloodlust run through my veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.64,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,But now, I'm afraid of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:26.79,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still doing my best, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:29.80,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Are you doing your best?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.65,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to praise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:35.53,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're great, Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:37.57,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:38.43,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.13,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:40.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:42.92,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.13,0:16:45.14,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:47.40,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:47.90,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Demon—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:52.41,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:54.23,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.23,0:16:57.66,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell have you been this past year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:57.66,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Ow! Wait! Ow! Stop hitting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I've been sending you reports!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:02.33,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Those are just picture diaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.40,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you ever come to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:08.25,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I've been busy with Gate City.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.11,0:17:12.13,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to figure how to get things into the Northern Fortress...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:14.63,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:18.72,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who ordered me to stop anything that could help the extremists.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:24.31,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You could just use your Ultimate Destruction magic to take care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:25.77,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:28.02,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone there is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.52,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,They're doing their best...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:31.48,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Every day, they cling to the slimmest hopes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:36.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just destroy them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.60,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:39.35,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The Fairy Queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:41.24,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,the beautiful forest songstresses,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:42.72,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,the Dragon Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.72,0:17:44.28,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The mechanoid girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:45.60,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,the girls at the tavern...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:47.75,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,All of them are trying their hardest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.16,0:17:50.25,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I can't destroy them just because I'm the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.65,0:17:55.19,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you weren't simply enjoying your popularity?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:57.09,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:59.01,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:01.10,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You're absolutely certain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:03.22,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:09.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you getting all kinds of passionate glances from nobles in the capital and rich merchants?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:12.19,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Head Maid, I told you not to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:13.63,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:17.44,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No, it wasn't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:20.57,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It was during a negotiation, like a duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.06,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.06,0:18:25.04,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Weakling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.62,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "weakling"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.50,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I was doing my best...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.92,0:18:30.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:32.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,flabby Demon King!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.34,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Flabby...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:37.72,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Flabby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.68,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say flabby?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.68,0:18:40.72,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Was it this mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:42.24,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,This mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:43.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts! Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:48.19,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I've been doing stretches and calisthenics every single day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:51.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Demon King, so why spend your time on something so petty?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:53.98,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It's not petty, you stupid Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:55.94,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're just a dumb recluse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:59.36,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And you're an idiot who can't even stay in one place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:06.58,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,The music of the New Year's festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:08.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Can I turn the lights on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:10.88,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:12.49,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You just suddenly returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I look like a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.84,0:19:15.95,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:18.15,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:19.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:21.24,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:22.97,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't put on any perfume.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:23.85,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.13,0:19:25.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:31.23,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You're always pretty and wonderful, so it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:36.37,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,How about a dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:45.27,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,If you'll take the lead...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.35,0:19:49.72,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:56.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.43,0:20:01.10,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Push out your chest a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.30,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get mad if I step on your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.94,0:20:08.60,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Half step to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:10.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And now the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:13.27,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.84,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I should've worn a nicer outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:20.73,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,You smell good, Demon King.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:23.64,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,And I feel safe in your arms, Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:26.04,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Is this enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:31.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, for your New Year's present...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:33.71,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.46,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:38.36,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't worry about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:40.42,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't expecting anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.21,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:45.92,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you want...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:47.68,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,As your owner, I could reward you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.19,0:20:49.56,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:52.25,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a lot of useless flesh,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:55.35,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,so maybe it's more a punishment than a reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:56.93,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:20:58.86,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.96,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.38,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:13.42,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we let go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:14.87,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.50,0:21:23.77,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing you gave me courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:25.31,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you don't want to see everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:26.46,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:28.47,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wait so long this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.89,0:21:31.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll retake Gate City in under a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:32.98,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:34.82,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Talking with you gave me an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.21,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:39.16,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The next time we meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:41.90,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be on a battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:44.28,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the sea as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:46.44,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fall behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:47.61,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:50.20,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I am your sword and your path.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.32,0:21:59.58,Default,M,0000,0000,0000,,You are
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my light.
